{"words":[{"word":"septimont","count":4},{"word":"blue","count":2},{"word":"furies","count":2},{"word":"ah","count":2},{"word":"folk","count":2},{"word":"alright","count":2},{"word":"te","count":2},{"word":"guardian","count":2},{"word":"arsinosa","count":2},{"word":"ha","count":1},{"word":"knew","count":1},{"word":"remain","count":1},{"word":"undefeated","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"write","count":1},{"word":"'em","count":1},{"word":"thinking","count":1},{"word":"sailors","count":1},{"word":"singers","count":1},{"word":"matter","count":1},{"word":"arena","count":1},{"word":"pure","count":1},{"word":"strength","count":1},{"word":"worried","count":1},{"word":"bets","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"times","count":1},{"word":"oh","count":1},{"word":"visitor","count":1},{"word":"welcome","count":1},{"word":"clothes","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"new","count":1},{"word":"federation","count":1},{"word":"i've","count":1},{"word":"met","count":1},{"word":"visitors","count":1},{"word":"huanglong","count":1},{"word":"proper","count":1},{"word":"polite","count":1},{"word":"tend","count":1},{"word":"speak","count":1},{"word":"riddles","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"hmm","count":1},{"word":"sounds","count":1},{"word":"familiar","count":1},{"word":"makin'","count":1},{"word":"jokes","count":1},{"word":"already","count":1},{"word":"style","count":1},{"word":"anyway","count":1},{"word":"enjoy","count":1},{"word":"stay","count":1},{"word":"friend","count":1},{"word":"watched","count":1},{"word":"live","count":1},{"word":"match","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"missed","count":1},{"word":"mattia","count":1},{"word":"gave","count":1},{"word":"team","count":1},{"word":"pounding","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"tricky","count":1},{"word":"folks","count":1},{"word":"solaris","count":1},{"word":"floodin'","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"lately","count":1},{"word":"half-human","count":1},{"word":"half-lion","count":1},{"word":"creature","count":1},{"word":"wearin'","count":1},{"word":"armor","count":1},{"word":"swingin'","count":1},{"word":"poleaxe","count":1},{"word":"gotta","count":1},{"word":"href","count":1},{"word":"echo","count":1},{"word":"lioness","count":1},{"word":"glory","count":1},{"word":"usually","count":1},{"word":"reveals","count":1},{"word":"great","count":1},{"word":"agon","count":1},{"word":"earn","count":1},{"word":"blessing","count":1},{"word":"highest","count":1},{"word":"honor","count":1},{"word":"any","count":1},{"word":"septimontian","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"finals","count":1},{"word":"held","count":1},{"word":"colosseum","count":1},{"word":"city","count":1},{"word":"dawdle","count":1},{"word":"ticket","count":1},{"word":"miss","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Ha, I knew it! The Blue Furies remain undefeated!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Ah, folk always write 'em off, thinking they're just sailors or singers. That don't matter in the arena. It's all about pure strength.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"So what? Worried about your bets? How many times do I have to—","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Alright, alright... Oh, look here, a visitor! Welcome to Septimont!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Your clothes aren't from around here. You from the New Federation?","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Ah, I've met some visitors from Huanglong before. Proper folk, polite as can be. They do tend to speak in riddles though!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Hmm... sounds familiar, but I can't say I know where that is.","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"Makin' jokes already? I like your style! Anyway, enjoy your stay here, friend!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"We just watched a live match. Too bad you missed it. Mattia from the Blue Furies gave the other team a right pounding!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"At this time? That might be tricky. Folks from all over Solaris are floodin' into Septimont lately!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"A half-human, half-lion creature wearin' armor and swingin' a poleaxe? That's gotta be the <te href=850168>Guardian Echo</te> of Septimont, our Lioness of Glory, Arsinosa!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"As the guardian of Septimont, Arsinosa usually only reveals herself during the Great Agon. To earn her blessing is the highest honor any Septimontian could hope for!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125},{"text":"If you want to see her, just wait for the finals. They'll be held in the Colosseum in the city. But don't dawdle, get a ticket now or you'll miss out!","quest_name":"Shadow of Glory","quest_id":125000125}]}